<p>How do I filter list by indexes stored in another list? For instance I have the following list of values:</p>  <pre><code>val list = List("a", "b", "c", "d", "e", "f") </code></pre>  <p>and the list of indexes:</p>  <pre><code>val indexes = List(1,2,5) </code></pre>  <p>I want to get the following list:</p>  <pre><code>List("b", "c", "f) </code></pre>  <p>What is the most idiomatic way?</p>